A minimalistic composition featuring a pristine white workspace with a single open laptop displaying an abstract flowing river of documentation pages streaming from the screen, transforming into origami paper birds that spiral upward. The birds gradually shift in color from deep indigo to soft teal, representing version-controlled documents taking flight. Beside the laptop sits a small potted bonsai tree with branches that subtly mirror the forking structure of code repositories. Clean geometric shadows cast across the scene from an unseen window, creating depth through negative space. The overall palette is muted whites, soft grays, and accent blues, evoking clarity, organization, and the seamless flow between code and documentation.
